name: BENE_ENRLMT_BGN_DT
comment: THE DATE THAT THE BENEFICIARY ENROLLED IN THE SERVICE ELECTION.[SOURCE: PLAN TRANSACTION, AUTOMATIC ENROLLMENT]

name: CNTRCT_PBP_SK
comment: AN IDR ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A VERSION OF A CONTRACT.

name: BENE_ENRLMT_APLCTN_DT
comment: BENEFICIARY ENROLLMENT APPLICATION DATE. DATE THE SERVICE DELIVERY ORGANIZATION RECEIVED THE ELECTION FORM FROM THE BENEFICIARY.

name: BENE_CVRG_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE OF COVERAGE IN WHICH THE BENEFICIARY IS ENROLLED.    REFERENCE TABLE: BENE_CVRG_TYPE_CD

name: BENE_ENRLMT_END_DT
comment: THE DATE THAT THE BENEFICIARY DISENROLLED IN THE SERVICE ELECTIONS .

name: BENE_DISENRLMT_RSN_CD
comment: THIS CODE IDENTIFIES THE REASON THAT A BENEFICIARY DISENROLLED IN A SERVICE ELECTION .

name: BENE_ENRLMT_SRC_CD
comment: THIS CODE IDENTIFIES THE SOURCE OF THE BENEFICIARYS ENROLLMENT.

name: BENE_ENRLMT_EMPLR_SBSDY_SW
comment: A SWITCH INDICATING THAT ENROLLMENT IN PART D WAS REQUESTED BY THE BENEFICIARY WHO HAS EMPLOYER SUBSIDY ENROLLMENT.

name: BENE_ELCTN_CCP_ENRLMT_MOS_NUM
comment: REPRESENTS THE NUMBER OF MONTHS A BENEFICIARY WAS ENROLLED IN A GIVEN MANAGED CARE ORGANIZATION (MCO) ON A COMMERCIAL BASIS, PRIOR TO THE MCOS MEDICARE CONTRACT.

name: SRC_AUDT_ID_SK
comment: IDENTIFIES THE SOURCE OF THE INFORMATION THAT CAUSED AN AUDIT ACTION TO OCCUR.

name: SRC_BGN_ID_SK
comment: THE USER ID OR SOURCE OF THE PERIOD START DATE.

name: SRC_END_ID_SK
comment: THE USER ID OR SOURCE OF THE PERIOD TERMINATION DATE.

name: BENE_ENRLMT_GRP_HLTH_PLAN_SW
comment: A SWITCH THAT INDICATES IF THE PLAN IS AN EMPLOYER GROUP HEALTH PLAN.

name: BENE_ENRLMT_OSA_SW
comment: THIS SWITCH INDICATES WHETHER THE MEDICARE BENEFICIARY HAS BEEN APPROVED FOR OUT OF SERVICE AREA ENROLLMENT

name: BENE_UI_APLCTN_RCPT_DT_DFLT_SW
comment: INDICATES IF, WHEN AN ENROLLMENT/PLAN CHANGE TRANSACTION IS SUBMITTED VIA THE UI BY CMS AUTHORIZED USERS, IF THE APPLICATION DATE WAS DEFAULTED TO EFFECTIVE DATE MINUS 2 DAYS. THIS IS INDICATED BY A VALUE OF Y. A SPACE WOULD APPLY FOR ALL OTHER SITUATIONS.

name: BENE_ENRLMT_CNTRCT_EFCTV_DT
comment: THE DATE THAT THE BENEFICIARY ENROLLED FOR THE FIRST TIME IN THE CONTRACT

name: META_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_LAST_UPDT_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS LOADED INTO THE IDR.    REFERENCE TABLE: V2_MDCR_META_DCTNRY_SRC

name: BENE_SRC_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER INDICATING WHERE THE SOURCE OF THE BENEFICIARY DATA IN THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ORIGINATED FROM.

name: BENE_INVLD_CNTRCT_NUM
comment: CAPTURES AN INVALID CONTRACT NUMBER

name: BENE_INVLD_PBP_NUM
comment: CAPTURES AN INVALID PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE NUMBER

name: BENE_ENRLMT_PGM_TYPE_CD
comment: THE TYPE OF PROGRAM SUCH AS HMOÒ², NURSING HOME CARE, LONG TERM CARE, WAIVERS FOR A BENEFICIARY.

name: BENE_PRIOR_DISENRLMT_RSN_CD
comment: WHEN A CANCELLATION IS REPORTED FOR A BENEFICIARY ACCOUNT THAT IS ALREADY DISENROLLED, THIS FIELD IS POPULATED WITH THE ORIGINAL DISENROLLMENT CODE.

name: BENE_CNTRCT_NUM
comment: UNIQUE IDENTIFIER ENABLING AN ENTITY TO PROVIDE COVERAGE TO ELIGIBLE MEDICARE BENEFICIARIES

name: BENE_PBP_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE IDENTIFIER FOR THE PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE OFFERED UNDER THE CONTRACT. FOR PART D THIS NUMBER IS A UNIQUE IDENTIFICATION FOR AN AGREEMENT BETWEEN CMS AND A PART D PROVIDER ENABLING THE PART D PROVIDER TO PROVIDE DRUG COVERAGE TO ELIGIBLE BENEFICIARIES. MARX DEFINITION: A 3-POSITION NUMERIC IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED TO A PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) OFFERED WITHIN A MANAGED CARE OR PRESCRIPTION DRUG CONTRACT. VALUES BEGINNING WITH 8 ARE RESERVED FOR EMPLOYER GROUP PLANS. A VALUE OF 999 IS RESERVED FOR COST CONTRACTORS WHO DO NOT CHOOSE TO OFFER A PRESCRIPTION DRUG BENEFIT

name: IDR_LTST_TRANS_FLG
comment: AN INDICATOR ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) THAT IDENTIFIES WHICH TRANSACTION RECORD, BASED ON PRIMARY KEY, IS CONSIDERED TO REPRESENT THE MOST RECENT RECORD RECEIVED FROM THE SOURCE.    Y = LATEST VERSION OF THE RECORD  N = PREVIOUS VERSION OF THE RECORD

name: META_SRC_PRCSG_ID
comment: A VALUE ASSIGNED BASED ON A BATCH IDENTIFICATION IN ORDER TO TRACE IT BACK TO ITS ORIGINAL SOURCE. IT WILL ONLY BE POPULATED WHEN A RECORD IS INSERTED.

name: META_LTST_SRC_PRCSG_ID
comment: A VALUE ASSIGNED BASED ON A BATCH IDENTIFICATION IN ORDER TO TRACE IT BACK TO ITS ORIGINAL SOURCE. IT WILL ONLY BE POPULATED WHEN A RECORD IS SUBSEQUENTLY UPDATED.

name: IDR_TRANS_OBSLT_TS
comment: THE SYSTEM DATE AND TIME ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) WHEN A RECORD WAS LAST KNOWN TO BE PRESENT IN THE SOURCE. THE CURRENT VERSION OF A RECORD WILL BE SET TO 12/31/9999 00:00:00.

name: IDR_INSRT_TS
comment: THE SYSTEM DATE AND TIME ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) WHILE PERFORMING AN INSERT OPERATION.

name: IDR_UPDT_TS
comment: THE SYSTEM DATE AND TIME ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) WHEN UPDATES ARE MADE TO ANY NON-PRIMARY KEY COLUMN.
